Introduction
------------

eMAILsearch is a fork of the open source reMail project.  reMail downloads all your email to your iPhone and searches it instantly.

This fork has added the following:

* Fixed build process that could not find openssl headers
* Landscape view

TODO items:

* Provide a way to lock the app via a pin code

